类 UnionCOperationParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mpos.lottery.te.gameimpl.union.game.UnionCOperationParameter
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class UnionCOperationParameter
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The settings of 'Triple' and 'Double' will be used to control risk. For example a single selected number of UNION may be:

    '1,2,3,4,5,6-2,4'

    Here the 'triple' part is '1,2,3,4,5,6', and the 'double' part is '2,4'. The semantics of setting UnionCOperationParameter is:

    if the count of numbers of 'triple' part is N(triple), then the count of numbers of 'double' part must between X(minDouble) and Y(maxDouble).
